
This document describes the test resources.

stories is the main directory for stories as per JBehave syntax

view is the main directory for view-related resources
view/ftl contains the Freemarker templates for generating JBehave reports
view/images contains images for the resulting report website
view/scripts contains scripts (js) for the resulting report website
view/styles contains CSS files for the resulting report website

Most of the view resources were taken and modified from the jbehave-core source code.

The view uses SyntaxHighlighter javascript/css source code - version 3.0.83